### Register User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Farmer",
  "email": "john@farm.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "location": "Lagos",
  "farmSize": 50
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@farm.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

